Group Home "Smart Home" ["Location"]
Group LivingRoom "Living Room" (Home) ["Location"]

Number Temperature "Temperature [%.1f °C]" (LivingRoom) ["Measurement","Temperature"]
Number Humidity "Humidity [%.1f %%]" (LivingRoom) ["Measurement","Humidity"]
Number LightLevel "Light [%d lx]" (LivingRoom) ["Measurement","Light"]

Switch Zigbee_Light "Zigbee Light" (LivingRoom) ["Light"]
Switch Zigbee_Fan "Zigbee Fan" (LivingRoom) ["Fan"]
Switch Zigbee_Socket "Zigbee Socket" (LivingRoom) ["Switch"]